		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Are there any special memory locations that are reserved between $0000 to $0800, besides the normal 6502 stuff? (zero page between $00-$FF, and the stack at $100-$1FF) I'm running my code on Michal Kowalski's 6502 simulator, and it runs fine, but when I try to run it on the "real thing" I get mixed results. I'm not using the PPU at all, just reading/writing to a memory location for I/O.

		

